===========================================
Simple Django keyword highlighter in a text
===========================================

Install
-------

`pip install dj-search-highlight`

Usage
-----
It is setup is very easy:

Settings
^^^^^^^^

.. code:: python

	INSTALLED_APPS = (
		# ...
		'highlighter',
	)


Template
^^^^^^^^

.. code:: html

	{% load highlight_yellow %}
	{{ some_text|highlight_yellow:keyword }}
